      • getParameterValue

        @Nullable
java.lang.Object getParameterValue(@NotNull
                                             java.lang.String parameterName)
        Gets the parameter value for parameter with given name.
        Parameters:
        parameterName - The name of the test run parameter
        Returns:
        The assigned value of the parameter. This method will return null if no value was set for the parameter or parameter with given name does not exist in this structure.
